  "id": "RAW_681784b4",
  "title": "ProductHunt 月榜快被华人“占满”了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTAwMzU1MA==&mid=2247504440&idx=1&sn=8b1612f9be7a54acf32c5be9f9ebaab4",
  "date": "2025-10-27 12:02:00",
  "author": "随机小分队",
  "siteName": "随机小分队",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\">\n      <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Product Hunt是全球最流行的发掘有意思新产品的平台。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\">经过近十年的发展，已经成为用户发现新产品、创业者获得灵感、投资人寻找新机会，以及创始人对产品进行推广的最好地方。</span></p>\n        <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">上个月的月榜中，华人产品“大杀四方”，在前十名占据八席，包含 AI 电商工具、视频工具、数据抓取/分析工具等各个方向。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">话不多说，下面就请来具体看看本期有趣的产品。</span></p>\n         <h3 style=\"margin:16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">1.VidAU：视频广告生成工具</span></span></h3>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">恭喜华人团队 VideoAU 荣膺榜首！</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统视频制作耗时长、成本高且需要多人团队参与。VidAU 将复杂的视频创作流程简化至几分钟，以极低成本为电商、营销人员和商业主提供高质量的视频广告解决方案，助力他们在社交媒体上快速推广。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">VidAU 的核心功能包括“产品图片转视频”，能将静态图片转为引人注目的生活方式视频或电影级片段；“AI UGC 视频”，利用 AI 数字人生成 UGC 风格的广告；以及“产品链接转视频”，通过一个产品链接快速生成多个视频广告方案。此外，“Product Video Remix”功能还支持批量生成适合 TikTok 的各种广告变体，方便 A/B 测试。</span></p>\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020778\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e51dc952&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8JGf7lL3sc8bnbHicmYqtu7RVwJibPscCTvftDn3ic6TV6quZPbtwW0N9onZD7OzoAgNicSfoWLPsNiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">VidAU 的定价为基于 Credits 定价，起步价为 29 美元/月，包含 150 Credits。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1,544</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：vidau.ai</span></p>\n         <h3 style=\"margin:16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">2.Ada：AI 数据分析工具</span></span></h3>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户在处理数据时，尝尝花费浪费大量时间在复制粘贴、手动获取和清洗数据，</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ada 是用户的 AI 数据分析师，可以将原始数据转化为专业、可操作报告。其核心功能包括“工作流程自动化”，用户只需设置一次，Ada 便能自动获取、清洗和更新数据；“分析和视觉智能”，不仅能生成精美图表和布局，还能进行深度分析，揭示趋势、关联性并提供可操作的洞察；以及“灵活的数据源”，支持混合网络抓取数据与自有数据进行更深层次的分析。</span></p>\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mh8n0tjh8z2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020779\" data-ratio=\"0.5994550408719346\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"734\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37e4c1ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8JGf7lL3sc8bnbHicmYqtu7UNqfdv01WAttJLgNvWs9Q4NegCAkkibYZXicyZia8D6icV49CCLicMeK6oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ada 提供免费版本，付费版定价为 40-200 美元/月，包含更多用量和 API 等功能。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;margin: 16px 0px 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">,</span><span leaf=\"\">465</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：ada.im</span></p>\n         <h3 style=\"margin:16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">3.Capalyze：AI 数据抓取工具</span></span></h3>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统方式进行数据抓取、分析和可视化效率低下。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">该产品主要面向需要实时真实数据的用户，如营销人员、卖家以及进行舆情研究的学生。其核心功能是“实时数据抓取”，将真实的网络数据抓取到其自有的电子表格引擎中，并通过电子表格 Agent，将用户提出的自然语言问题分解并分配给专业的 Agent 执行抓取、数据分析、情感分析、数据丰富和可视化等任务，最终以交互式表格和图表的形式交付结果。</span></p>\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020780\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ba167fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8JGf7lL3sc8bnbHicmYqtu7BUMXLdcTojHngTSBEvPjiaJlnPMDwdbwkSxROcU2LKiamEHK1gwR7ib7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Capalyze 提供免费版本，付费版定价为 9.9-25 美元/月，包含更多用量和高级分析。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;margin: 16px 0px 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">,</span><span leaf=\"\">227</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：capalyze.ai</span></p>\n         <h3 style=\"margin:16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">4.Person search API：真人搜索 API</span></span></h3>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Crustdata 的“人物搜索 API ”旨在解决真人数据陈旧的问题。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这款 API 主要面向 AI Agent 和内部/外部招聘平台、AI 投资平台和内部销售平台等。其核心功能是提供超过 60 种过滤条件，允许用户通过一次 API 调用，即可编程化地、精准地在网络上搜索并完善人物数据。</span></p>\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\