:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CREAO 提供免费版本；付费版定价为25美元/月，包含 Agent 、定制的 API 和 MCP 集成等功能。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;margin: 16px 0px 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">,</span><span leaf=\"\">128</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：creao.ai</span></p>\n         <h3 style=\"margin:16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">6.YouMind：AI 驱动的内容创作工具</span></span></h3>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多人都有值得创造的想法，但将这些“火花”转化为完整的文章、播客、视频等成品往往是一个具有挑战性的过程。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px