-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CapCut AI Suite 的核心功能是“AI 智能编辑”，包括“提示词到创作”，用户只需描述想法，CapCut 即可在几秒内生成包含脚本、视觉效果和音乐的完整视频。其特色功能还包括：利用 Veo3、Seedance 和 Seedream 等模型进行AI媒体生成；AutoCut、AI Clipper 和转录工具等智能编辑工具；将照片转化为逼真、富有表现力的动画角色的 AI 数字人与角色；以及可一键实现视频多语言翻译的 AI 视频翻译器。</span></p>\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020787\" data-ratio=\"0.5626598465473146\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"782\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=427e907c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8JGf7lL3sc8bnbHicmYqtu7ibIGdpN9hJ8EgicQPzQe6Q2aMF8GibaQPGSRVLWIs33PaW5AW8qia7ZwGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n         <figure style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"></figure>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CapCut 可免费使用，Pro 版本 19.99 美元/月。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：891</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:16px 0px 10px;white-s